long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This browser extension sets https://dashboardify.app/Dashboardify/ as your default home page and new tab page. 

This web app allows you to create customizable dashboards, with unlimited numbers of bookmarks / links pinned on the screen (in any position), as well as Notes, IFrames, HTML embeds, and other features.

Users can also resize the widgets and/or drag them around the screen in real time, as well as setup multiple different dashboards.
